        default: Location Id
    dhs-correlationId:

      description: DHS Correlation ID
      schema:
        type: string
        default: urn:uuid:LOC00001a72594485d924214
    dhs-productId:
      name: dhs-productId
      required: true
      in: header
      description: DHS Product ID
